[#title#]
Determines if a string is a palindrome

[#description#]
This function returns 1 if the string passed as parameter is a palindrome or 0 otherwise. Please note that we will ignore case, punctuation and spaces in determining whether the string is a palindrome. "Dammit, I'm mad!" is a palindrome by this definition.

